name: SEMAR
description:
Semar has a very unique physical form, as if he is a symbol of the depiction of the universe. Its round body is a symbol of the earth, where humans and other creatures live. Semar is always smiling, but with puffy eyes. This depiction as a symbol of joy and sorrow. His face is old but his hair is cut in a bun like a child, as a symbol of old and young. He is male, but has breasts like a girl, as a symbol of man and woman. He was the incarnation of a god but lived as a commoner, as a symbol of superiors and subordinates.
